  "notes": "This is a Drupal Layout Builder block for page-level media. The picture element always has exactly four source elements targeting: (1) large desktop (min-width:1280px) two-thirds width, (2) desktop full width (min-width:1024px), (3) tablet two-thirds (min-width:768px), and (4) mobile fallback. Each source has a 1x and 2x srcset entry. The figcaption is optional — only present in a minority of samples. The root element carries Drupal block classes: 'block block-layout-builder block-field-blocknodepagefield-b-media'. The img uses loading='eager' and fixed width/height of 375x211 for mobile.",
